== Support ==
If you have any questions or comments please get in touch at support@airlockdigital.com
If you have any ideas for new dashboard views that you would like to see, please let us know!
https://www.airlockdigital.com

== Splunk Requirements ==
Airlock Digital Add-On - https://splunkbase.splunk.com/app/5674/

== Troubleshooting ==
No data displayed?
1) Please ensure the 'airlock index' macro is set appropriately 
2) If you are sending data from Airlock, please ensure the sourcetype is set with a name of 'airlock:hec'.